# TRANSIT

This widget will involve place-specific, real-time information and potentially many APIs

For a given time, location, and destination, users:

+ Should be able to see their **options for traveling** from the current location to the desired destination(s)

+ Should be notified of any **noteworthy conditions** such as traffic accidents or system delays

+ Should be informed of the **best option**

+ Should be given **notification when departure is needed** to utilize best option
